# Dompet App

Aplikasi keuangan personal.

## Tech Stack
- Backend: Python + FastAPI (port 8080)
- Frontend: React + TypeScript + Vite (port 5174)
- Database: PostgreSQL

## Setup

### Backend
\`\`\`bash
cd backend
cp .env.example .env
# isi .env dengan nilai yang sesuai
uv sync
uv run alembic upgrade head
uv run python seed.py
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8080
\`\`\`

### Frontend
\`\`\`bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
\`\`\`